        <para>

        </para>
        <itemizedlist>
            <listitem>
                <para>
                    <emphasis role="bold">Inherit</emphasis>
                </para>
                <para> If no, then it inherits the event from event input port, elseif yes, then event is activated by regular input port.</para>
                <para> Properties : Type 'vec' of size 1. </para>
